    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .Normal {className: Normal; margin-bottom: 8pt;}\n.html-preview .ListParagraph {font-family: 'Times New Roman';}\n.html-preview .ConsPlusNonformat {font-family: 'Courier New'; font-size: 10pt;}\n.html-preview .TableGrid td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 299.56786703601px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 321.70637119114px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Фуқаролик ишлари бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">{#2}Ариза берилган фуқаролик суди номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> судига</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 299.56786703601px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\" width: 321.70637119114px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-5\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#5}Даъвогарнинг яшаш манзили</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">да яшовчи</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 299.56786703601px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\" width: 321.70637119114px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 299.56786703601px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\" width: 321.70637119114px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Телефон: </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#7}Даъвогарнинг телефон рақами</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 299.56786703601px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 4=\"\" style=\" width: 321.70637119114px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Электрон почта манзили: </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#8}Даъвогарнинг электрон манзили</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Д<span class=\"leading\"></span>А Ъ В О <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>А Р И З А</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">(Дастлабки синов муддатини бекор қилиш юзасидан)</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Мен </span><span class=\"structures structure-10\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#10} Даъвогар ишга кирган сана</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> йилда </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Даъвогар ишга кирган ташкилот номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> ташкилотига </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#12}Даъвогар ишга тайинланган лавозим</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> лавозимига ишга тайинландим. Менинг уч ёшга етмаган фарзандим бор ва мен яна ҳомиладорман. Аммо ишга кирганимдан бошлаб уч ой давомида менга ойлик берилмади бунинг сабабини ташкилот бухгалтеридан сўраганимда менга нисбатан синов муддати белгиланганлиги <span class=\"leading\"></span>ва бу даврда ойлик маош берилмаслигини айтди.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Бироқ янги таҳрирдаги Меҳнат кодексининг 129-моддасига кўра, ҳомиладор аёл, уч ёшга тўлмаган боласи бор аёл ёки уч ёшга тўлмаган болани ёлғиз ўзи тарбиялаётган ота (васий)га дастлабки синов муддати белгиланмаслиги <span class=\"leading\"></span>белгиланган.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">Юқоридаги қоидага ва бошқа қонун ҳужжатларига асосланиб,</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: center; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">СЎРАЙМАН:</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#11}Даъвогар ишга кирган ташкилот номи</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; color: #000000;\"> ташкилоти томонидан менга нисбатан тайинланган дастлабки синов муддатини бекор қилишингизни ва шу муддатда менга берилиши лозим бўлган ойлик маошимни олишимда амалий ёрдам беришингизни.</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\"> <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>Илова:</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify; text-indent: 37.8px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#13}Илова қилинаётган ҳужжатлар рўйхати</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"border: 0px solid; border-spacing: 0; \">\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 291.85595567867px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt; font-weight: bold;\">Даъвогар:</span><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-6\" style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">{#6}Даъвогарнинг Ф.И.О.си</span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 122.32686980609px;\">\n<p> </p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 0; width: 207.09141274238px;\">\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 14pt;\">___________</span></p>\n<p class=\"ConsPlusNonformat\" style=\" text-align: cent